  <Overview>Gameyfin is a simple manager for your game library&#xD;
&#xD;
IGDB account is required in order to fetch games metadata from the database&#xD;
&#xD;
How to obtain API token:&#xD;
==============================&#xD;
Read docs: https://api-docs.igdb.com/#about&#xD;
==============================&#xD;
1. Sign Up with Twitch for a free account&#xD;
2. Ensure you have Two Factor Authentication enabled&#xD;
3. Register your application&#xD;
4. Manage your newly created application&#xD;
5. Generate a Client Secret by pressing "New Secret"&#xD;
6. Take note of the Client ID and Client Secret</Overview>
